{"tid":982819,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"寄養兔雙耳現可疑傷口　有兔子營養不良卻沒求醫　賓紛會被指不當照顧兔兔","createTime":"2019-01-15T12:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T06:24:51.000Z","uid":74247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce2e25b324c362316ebca627394e1d0fa5ecb14b","tid":982819,"uid":74247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:09:34.000Z","msg":"【動物專訊】經營兔兔寄養酒店的賓紛會，被多名兔友質疑不當照顧兔兔，兔兔「丁丁」在寄養期間兩耳出現可疑傷口，而主人已去世的兔兔「無名」在12月時開始消瘦，兔友在1月6日將牠接走送醫後發現牠嚴重營養不良，但賓紛會之前只為牠灌食草粉，沒有帶牠看醫生，「無名」更於翌日去世。賓紛會負責人Wing Sir回應本報查詢時強調，發現「無名」沒吃草後已盡力照顧及為牠灌食草粉，及聯絡牠已故主人的妹妹尋求指示，但對方沒正面回應指示要看獸醫。至於丁丁的事件，他則以警方正調查為由不作評論。<br />\n<br />\n現時法例沒有嚴格規管動物寄養所的照顧方法，政府將進行的《動物福利法》諮詢，據知將引入照顧動物的謹慎責任，短期照顧動物的寄養所可能會受新法規管。兔子丁丁的主人Zoe表示，希望藉賓紛會這兩宗事件，讓更多人參與1月20日的遊行，發聲表達要求政府就動物福利全面立法的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkanimalpost.com/2019/01/15/01152/?fbclid=IwAR0p8qZL2GSpU_8NBX0dqFTypBeKptUsBpjfHRnQuAU_v_1BFHoBJlfcT4k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkanimalpost.com%2F2019%2F01%2F15%2F01152%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0p8qZL2GSpU_8NBX0dqFTypBeKptUsBpjfHRnQuAU_v_1BFHoBJlfcT4k&d=YyosyXkv3krQ3%2BbqA6FPNFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=b3ba38cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkanimalpost.com/2019/01/15/01152/?fbclid=IwAR0p8qZL2GSpU_8NBX0dqFTypBeKptUsBpjfHRnQuAU_v_1BFHoBJlfcT4k</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfcbc76c40a83a99c5780f54ec5cb11a7fee242","tid":982819,"uid":160439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c729d873078c7d7bfff2efaf61ec93041ac00f3e","tid":982819,"uid":74247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dcfcbc76c40a83a99c5780f54ec5cb11a7fee242","tid":982819,"uid":160439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bcb1bf624883d863e3f7bae9e3ec71ac8966c7","tid":982819,"uid":170370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻兔早已變棄兔，我懷疑有人扮好心唔將隻兔送去兔協。然後有事又唔帶佢去左睇醫生，只係一味賴落已故主人個妹度。果個妹根本就唔想認隻兔，佢問黎把鬼？<br />\n我知佢係做生意，唔係開善堂。冇野咖，咁佢就唔好扮好人，一早送走去兔協咪得，冇人會怪佢喎。<br />\n推到上蘋果<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc26e2ee070784a0cc8c3ca76c036d37889945f","tid":982819,"uid":74247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:08:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff98a4996af7a7bf2e33b71b22e8349f5e21e50","tid":982819,"uid":231089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T18:18:49.000Z","msg":"放過兔仔係佢到寄養，好彩冇事！！依家都唔敢再去寄養了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6dc250e5afa438a6ee8662bc52153a3f2d2f00","tid":982819,"uid":74247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor